    m_PersistentCalls:
      m_Calls: []
  m_text: 'Abilities:

    1, 2, & 3 - Activate/Cancel Ability

    1 - Rifle Shot
    (Point & Click)

    2 - Raining Blood (Circle AOE)

    3 - Sneaky Sweep (Cone
    AOE & Bonus damage in shadows)

    Enter - End Turn

    Tab - Inventory

    Shift
    - Show Visiblity Features

    Space - Flip coin when targeting ability to increase
    damage on success but decrease damage on fails


    WASD - Move Camera

    Left
    Click - Move/Confirm

    Right Click - Rotate Camera'
